<br>
  We started out as &quot;The Harmonium&quot; and went thru a couple of complete reformations to clear out alts and such of people who had left the guild.  (/hug Guild Management tool...  Porting around the world trying to find a guilded alt of someone who had quit/sold/etc to remove them when they wouldn't tell you where they were was quite annoying :P)  We flip-flopped back and forth between &quot;The Harmonium&quot; and &quot;Harmonium&quot; a couple of times.<br>
<br>
  When DAoC came out some Harm folks went and started a guild there (Harmonium on Hibernia/Palomides) and the next &quot;removal reformation&quot; changed the guild name to &quot;Legends of Harmonium&quot; from an EQ standpoint, but our website never reflected that change.<br>
<br>
  A few months back we switched yet again back to &quot;Harmonium&quot; (or is it &quot;The Harmonium&quot; <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   )<br>
<br>
  Of the original 10 folks who formed the guild, I am the only one still playing EQ now, but many, many of our current members are from way back in the pre-kunark days. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=355122"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.harmonium.net/filespace/sekira/seksig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub228.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sekiraashdelane>Sekira Ashdelane</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif" BORDER=0> at: 10/15/03 9:08 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub228.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=drinnicus>Drinnicus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#330000>(10/16/03 7:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=994.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Old Guild</span><hr size=1> ... <p>&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=749218&quot;&gt;Drinnicus Soulblader&lt;/a&gt;<br>
