<br>
Harmonium was the 1st guild on Xev. Our original guildleader quit EQ and some problems were caused as far as appointing new officers etc, so the guild reformed under the name Legends of Harmonium. However, the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>original</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> guild Harmonium was never actually deleted.<br>
<br>
GM's were made aware that we were unpleased with the name Legends Of Harmonium and that we wanted our original name of Harmonium back. I suspect that when we were finally given the name Harmonium back, we regained our seniority. <p>Sage Flintnilf Ironori<br>
Harmonium, Xev<br>
